      "raw_text": "The Spokane Falls Typographical\nunion yesterday appointed a COM\nmittee to work in conjunction with\nlike committees from the bookbind-\ners and pressmen in getting up a\ndance of the printing trades of Spo-\nkane. 1t is proposed to hold an\nannual ball in the future and to\nmake the event one of the big So\ncial features of local labor.\n\n\nThe typos also gave the dele\ngates who have been in attendance\nat the meetings of local unions\nwhich have been considering the\norganization of a new central body,\ncredentials to represent the union\nin the new organization, which will\nprobably be launched at the next\nmeeting to be held Sunday, Feb. II."
    }
